{"tid":1839140,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(東區已罷）好多醫護一直都好支持我哋 今次到我哋支持返佢哋","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T10:46:02.000Z","uid":91205,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a55225ce126979ac819ccd72af48db709728610","tid":1839140,"uid":91205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:45:56.000Z","msg":"本人聲明<br />\n絕對支持醫護人員罷工<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎至今擴散至多個國家<br />\n各國亦因應情況開始實施出入境限制<br />\n然而香港政府依然對病毒散播的危機視若無睹<br />\n香港市民經歷過2003年沙士的肆虐<br />\n眼見多名醫護人員捨身救亡<br />\n17年後政府不但莫視肺炎感染危機<br />\n更再次把醫護人員置於死地<br />\n視其生命如草芥<br />\n本人在此聲明<br />\n會為自己健康狀況負責任<br />\n全力支持醫護人員罷工<br />\n直至政府作出相應措施<br />\n尤其是停止高鐵站運作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5K0pnRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5K0pnRA.jpg&h=bc394bbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72ad4966d98c574b0edfea125c9345f62d9ee987","tid":1839140,"uid":76922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LS0kFCe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLS0kFCe.png&h=7c434027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港醫護唔罷工 結果會係咁"},{"pid":"00c1a9cf66bd4cabd4d87f8617be4e5312fbe23d","tid":1839140,"uid":91205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9da5a64de1c905d29b65da344fcae59d5bd840","tid":1839140,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"罷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e471fca658cbca7eeb1c31